hopobject.body: A pension scheme nutrex lipo 6 My life is a tribute to the American Dream. My business partner and I started with 300 record albums and a $20 booth at the local farmers market. That was nearly 34 years ago. Vintage Vinyl has grown into a multi-million dollar company with 23 employees. We stage 150 in-store concerts a year in our 7,500 square-foot store. With tens of thousands of compact discs, records and DVDs, we're the largest independent music store in the Midwest.
